transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling. This is John. How can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Hi there. Hey, I just had a couple of questions.

Speaker 1: Well, I ordered some yesterday, but I've also seen some reviews that say that this isn't even actually real Viagra.

Speaker 2: What is it?

Speaker 1: It's real Viagra, sir.

Speaker 2: We sell all FDA-approved medication, whether we sell Arcialis or Viagra, it's all FDA-approved real medication.

Speaker 1: Okay, it is. Okay.

Speaker 2: Because I know you guys say a bunch of stuff about a lot of other places, and I don't know.

Speaker 1: I haven't really seen much about you, but I'm just kind of curious about this.

Speaker 2: Oh, I understand, and I know how the marketing is and stuff.

Speaker 1: Just to kind of make it a little simpler, a lot of other companies, what they do is they sell compounded drugs,

Speaker 2: and they have their own pharmacy making it for them.

Speaker 1: We're buying these from the manufacturers of the pharmaceuticals, and they're all FDA-approved.

Speaker 2: So it is a real thing.

Speaker 1: Okay. Hey, okay, could you tell me this then?

Speaker 2: I mean, it doesn't really say when I sign in.

Speaker 1: It just says something about in the pharmacy.

Speaker 2: Do you know how long it's going to take?

Speaker 1: You said you ordered yesterday?

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: You usually get the pills typically five to seven days from the day you ordered it.

Speaker 2: You should have it probably next Tuesday or so, around then.

Speaker 1: Okay, because it doesn't really say anything yet.

Speaker 2: So if it says at pharmacy, that means it's processing at the pharmacy, so you've been approved.

Speaker 1: Once it's done processing, they'll ship it to your home directly.

Speaker 2: Usually it takes a couple days once they ship it.

Speaker 1: So I would expect it to be shipped out tomorrow.

Speaker 2: Okay, does it say anything?

Speaker 1: Oh, it does provide a tracking number?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Once it officially ships, there will be a tracking number not only on your profile,

Speaker 2: but it will be emailed to you as well, and it's through the postal service.

Speaker 1: Postal service.

Speaker 2: Okay, all right then.

Speaker 1: And, well, okay, I just kind of, I don't know.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: I'll try it, see if it works.

Speaker 2: Okay, all right then.

Speaker 1: Okay, thanks.

Speaker 2: Okay, thanks.

Speaker 1: Bye.
